- Installation instructions for cluedo game assistant -

<https://github.com/VictorDenisov/cluedo>

Last update: February 3, 2013

REQUIREMENTS
------------

* GHC-7.4.1 - is recommended. Earlier versions are untested.
* Cabal-1.17.0 - is recommended. Earlier versions are untested.

RUNNING UNDER LINUX
-------------------

Run

  # cabal configure
  # cabal build.

If you want to run cluedo without installation then use
  # ./run.sh.

If you want to install cluedo use:
  # cabal install
